'''Patijak Sonn''' was the [[Author/Legends|author]] of the [[Book/Legends|book]] ''[[Kholemi Elaru]]''. For a [[Time/Legends|time]], it was the fourth best-selling book on a list compiled by [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News's]] [[HoloNet News CoCo District Edition|CoCo Town Edition]] on the [[Great ReSynchronization|date]] [[23 BBY/Legends|13:2:28]].<ref name="HNN">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|45||A Closer Look}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Patijak Sonn was mentioned in [[HoloNet News Vol. 531 45|''HoloNet News Vol. 531 #45'']], a<ref name="HNN" /> [[2002]]<ref name="JCF">{{JCFCite|url=threads/5990764|board=Literature|thread=The Official HoloNetNews Discussion Thread|archiveurl=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/dY0zn}}</ref> [[in-universe]] [[HoloNet News (original website)|website]].<ref name="HNN" /> [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[Paul Ens]] wrote the site content.<ref name="HNN Credits">{{HoloNetNewsWeb||credits.html|Credits}}</ref>

